  // Would it take an action or something similar to activate the blindsight property of a Dragon Mask?
  // SKIP: The spec models action economy (pUseAction, freeInteractionUsed, etc.) but has no mechanism
  // for magic item activation or blindsight as a condition/sense. The accepted answer is purely a DM
