  // Source: https://rpg.stackexchange.com/q/190809
  
  // SKIP: Q&A resolves to a DM ruling with no deterministic PHB answer; the spec has no functions modeling Wall of Force, See Invisibility, or spell-specific line-of-sight interactions through barriers.

